    <thetext>6.1.7.3 Invariants of the Essential Internal Methods

[[GetOwnProperty]] (P)

4th bullet point:
---
If P’s attributes other than [[Writable]] may change over time or if the property might disappear, then P’s [[Configurable]] attribute must be true.
---


That description is not quite correct: The [[Value]] attribute may change if [[Configurable]] = false and [[Writable]] = true.</thetext>
